# ðŸ§  Real-World Concepts Practiced

| Concept | Real-Time Application | Extension Idea |
|---------|-----------------------|----------------|
| Random number generation | Simulating customer data, financial returns | Add more distributions (Poisson for events, exponential for waiting times) |
